---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="lifeGLANCE"
  description="Your life, at a glance. lifeGLANCE helps you see the shape of your life across weeks, months, and years. Goals, habits, milestones: curated, not cluttered."
  ogImage="/og/lifeglance.svg"
>
  <article class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 md:py-28">
    <!-- Breadcrumb -->
    <nav class="mb-10 font-sans text-sm text-glance-dim" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-glance-muted transition-colors">GLANCE Apps</a>
      <span class="mx-2">/</span>
      <span class="text-glance-muted">lifeGLANCE</span>
    </nav>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
      <div>
        <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-6xl font-semibold leading-none mb-4">
          <span class="text-glance-muted font-medium">life</span><span style="color: #7b70db;" class="tracking-wider font-bold">GLANCE</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-glance-muted font-serif italic mb-8">
          Your life, at a glance.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-5 text-glance-muted font-serif text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10">
          <p>
            Most life-tracking apps turn your goals into a to-do list. lifeGLANCE
            takes a different approach: it helps you see the shape of your life
            across weeks, months, and years.
          </p>
          <p>
            Define what matters to you. Track it gently. Review it without judgment.
            lifeGLANCE is a place to zoom out, to notice patterns, celebrate progress,
            and remember what you're working toward.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
          <a
            href="https://lifeglance.app"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-sans text-sm font-semibold px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg transition-colors duration-150"
            style="background-color: #7b70db; color: #0D0D12;"
          >
            Visit lifeglance.app ↗
          </a>
          <a
            href="/apps/lifeglance/downloads"
            class="font-sans text-sm text-glance-muted hover:text-glance-text transition-colors duration-150"
            style="color: #7b70db80;"
          >
            All downloads →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-glance-surface border border-glance-border-dim rounded-xl p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xs font-sans font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-glance-dim mb-5">
            What it does
          </h2>
          <ul class="space-y-4 font-sans text-sm text-glance-muted">
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span style="color: #7b70db;" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0">◆</span>
              <span><strong class="text-glance-text font-medium">Life areas</strong>: Organize what matters: health, work, relationships, creativity, and more.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span style="color: #7b70db;" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0">◆</span>
              <span><strong class="text-glance-text font-medium">Goal tracking</strong>: Set intentions and watch them unfold over time.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span style="color: #7b70db;" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0">◆</span>
              <span><strong class="text-glance-text font-medium">Habit streaks</strong>: Quiet, pressure-free consistency tracking.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span style="color: #7b70db;" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0">◆</span>
              <span><strong class="text-glance-text font-medium">Milestones</strong>: Mark and remember the things worth celebrating.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-glance-surface border border-glance-border-dim rounded-xl p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xs font-sans font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-glance-dim mb-4">
            Platforms
          </h2>
          <p class="font-sans text-sm text-glance-muted">Web · Android · macOS · Windows · Linux · iOS (soon)</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 pt-10 section-rule">
      <h2 class="text-xs font-sans font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-glance-dim mb-6">
        Privacy
      </h2>
      <p class="font-sans text-sm text-glance-muted max-w-xl leading-relaxed mb-4">
        lifeGLANCE stores all your data locally on your device. No account
        required. No data sent to our servers. Your life overview is yours.
      </p>
      <a href="/privacy" class="font-sans text-sm text-glance-accent link-underline">
        Privacy policy →
      </a>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
